access-password-regeneratebyid

For Admin panel only. Regenerates a users password to a temporary password. Then the password is marked as expired so they will be forced to update it when they next login.

Note: This will return an error if the user signed up via LinkedIn.

Authorizations:
cookieAuthApiKeyAuthJwtAuth
Request Body schema: application/json
required
id
required
integer

The users id.

versionauthor
integer <int64>
